ice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/142255_923f1babe5f9e116335c2f140d533a36.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F142255_923f1babe5f9e116335c2f140d533a36.JPG&h=848b166c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲用緊!</blockquote><br />\n有專用制得停， 播音樂， 好方便"},{"pid":"c31c3795e89bd4cdc1e8bbc209792e49c779fad2","tid":475814,"uid":100078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T08:53:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/142255_923f1babe5f9e116335c2f140d533a36.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F142255_923f1babe5f9e116335c2f140d533a36.JPG&h=848b166c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲用緊!</blockquote><br />\nKEEP到好新淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係1999 - 2000年左右買既, 好記得阿媽埋單要成一皮野<br />\n我當時係小學雞,打去CS問點解電腦冇WORD 同EXCEL 既? 好白痴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家得返個KEYBOARD 仲建在, 返工用, 真心好用!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cba6330b67c9820753875abcb4d382fa082ccdf","tid":475814,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:08:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果時tiny d機又平又多野送</blockquote><br />\n我都係2000年買， 成皮， 但乜柒都包哂<br />\n主機，厚mon(好戇鳩，遲一排就出薄mon),  眼仔， scanner,  printer,  喇叭。<br />\n部野都用到5年</blockquote><br />\n當年送Game RCT1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己第一隻PC game</blockquote><br />\n果時佢同IBM都做緊promotions <br />\n主機加1蚊有 scanner printer mon</blockquote><br />\n咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240bc4e37e4478af2f873a9efd906401b6892ac4","tid":475814,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果時tiny d機又平又多野送</blockquote><br />\n我都係2000年買， 成皮， 但乜柒都包哂<br />\n主機，厚mon(好戇鳩，遲一排就出薄mon),  眼仔， scanner,  printer,  喇叭。<br />\n部野都用到5年</blockquote><br />\n當年送Game RCT1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己第一隻PC game</blockquote><br />\n仲記得用個白色碟套入住<br />\n個陣送左四隻game 唯獨淨係記得RCT1</blockquote><br />\n嗰陣得56k 細個唔識買game<br />\n唔係玩接龍彈珠台就係玩呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7abbb737478acfd312dd8252b9a5dd876c7e03","tid":475814,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/22/142255_923f1babe5f9e116335c2f140d533a36.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F22%2F142255_923f1babe5f9e116335c2f140d533a36.JPG&h=848b166c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲用緊!</blockquote><br />\nTiny <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTiny電腦結業客戶追貨無門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本報訊】全港最大的個人電腦零售連鎖店 Tiny（泰來）電腦日前突然停業，並即時解僱約八十名員工，員工指公司未有支付通知金及遣散費等估計達過百萬元的補償，已向勞工處求助。有市民上星期剛付八千元訂金購買電腦，仍未取貨，又無法聯絡泰來負責人，擔心無法追回貨款，已向消費者委員會求助。 <br />\n市民陳小姐稱，上星期二在鑽石山荷里活廣場的 Tiny分店選購電腦送給父親，當時售貨員還表示公司正擴展，她也以為大公司「信得過」，並以現金支付了七千多元的大部份貨款，至上周末從報章得悉該公司停業，連日來多番嘗試聯絡該公司都無人接聽，她已向消委會求助，並考慮報警。<br />\n<br />\n53僱員勞工處求助<br />\nTiny電腦的用戶陳太則向本報表示，年前以萬多元買機時另付千多元作保用費，早前電腦故障交由 Tiny維修，近日卻無法聯絡該公司，至昨日其丈夫親到 Tiny北角的寫字樓查詢，才獲職員將電腦交還。 <br />\n勞工處至昨日共接獲五十三名泰來電腦的僱員求助，涉及被解僱的賠償問題，處方將為勞資雙方安排調解會議。泰來員工張先生說，上星期五全體同事共約八十人突被召返公司寫字樓，通知他們公司自兩年前開始虧蝕，決定清盤，即時向他們派發二月份至當日的薪金，卻沒有給他們計算佣金、代通知金、遣散費、公積金等補償，令突然失業的他十分不滿。 <br />\n成衣業文職及零售業職工總會權益及投訴主任張添財表示，接獲十多名 Tiny員工的求助，工會已建議他們保留薪金、年資等證明，日後可能需要申請公司清盤，並從破產欠薪保障基金申領補償。有公司職員指， Tiny的老闆兼營紅酒等其他業務，其他業務的生意不俗。<br />\n<br />\n部份分店仍有存貨<br />\n記者昨日曾前往 Tiny多間分店，全已關門停業，部份仍貼出盤點「休息一天」的告示，店內仍有存貨，一些電腦仍然開啟。至於位於北角柯達大廈二期的 Tiny公司寫字樓，昨日上址已轉為一家紅酒公司，該公司的職員指 Tiny已遷走，大廈「水牌」也取消了 Tiny的名稱。 <br />\n來自英國的 Tiny於九七年四月進軍本港，爭奪個人電腦巿場，並採取直銷連鎖形式經營，藉此降低零售價搶客，在港分店一度達二十多間。 <br />\n醫管局港島西醫院聯網發言人表示，瑪麗醫院及東華醫院有數台 Tiny電腦供辦公室使用，但保養及維修服務由醫院的資訊科技組支援，因此病人服務不受影響。</blockquote><br />\n原來係執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d012bab17c67af0297d89e370f0244080c5076c7","tid":475814,"uid":48321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果時tiny d機又平又多野送</blockquote><br />\n我都係2000年買， 成皮， 但乜柒都包哂<br />\n主機，厚mon(好戇鳩，遲一排就出薄mon),  眼仔， scanner,  printer,  喇叭。<br />\n部野都用到5年</blockquote><br />\n當年送Game RCT1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己第一隻PC game</blockquote><br />\n仲記得用個白色碟套入住<br />\n個陣送左四隻game 唯獨淨係記得RCT1</blockquote><br />\n嗰陣得56k 細個唔識買game<br />\n唔係玩接龍彈珠台就係玩呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年在元朗廣場買，仲記得佢啲demo機係玩類似賓尼兔的遊戲，果時買機係送盜墓者羅拉"},{"pid":"065780093b26bac8b913feec82226196e8040f6d","tid":475814,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:35:20.000Z","msg":"a 牌同價好咁多😂唉"},{"pid":"74ccc1ac2c0c208e5bff23e7fb383103d9c1f7d5","tid":475814,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T11:35:41.000Z","msg":"4千銀 tft mon😂😨"},{"pid":"f3cab9c594644d7bc96fbb2613d38017bda9df51","tid":475814,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果時tiny d機又平又多野送</blockquote><br />\n我都係2000年買， 成皮， 但乜柒都包哂<br />\n主機，厚mon(好戇鳩，遲一排就出薄mon),  眼仔， scanner,  printer,  喇叭。<br />\n部野都用到5年</blockquote><br />\n當年送Game RCT1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己第一隻PC game</blockquote><br />\n仲記得用個白色碟套入住<br />\n個陣送左四隻game 唯獨淨係記得RCT1</blockquote><br />\n嗰陣得56k 細個唔識買game<br />\n唔係玩接龍彈珠台就係玩呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年在元朗廣場買，仲記得佢啲demo機係玩類似賓尼兔的遊戲，果時買機係送盜墓者羅拉</blockquote><br />\n唔知依家廠機仲有無咁多野送呢"},{"pid":"2ddddeb6fc1facb7093a5e4baec87ac1e720c240","tid":475814,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我屋企都仲用屋緊q6600<br />\n<br />\n都成10年 唔打機 只係上網 睇劇 都仲用得</blockquote><br />\n神U榜榜首<br />\n<br />\n以下為我記得既其餘超頻神U：<br />\n<br />\nCeleron 300A<br />\n<br />\nPentium III 500E<br />\n<br />\nAMD 2500+<br />\n<br />\nAMD Phenom II X710<br />\n<br />\nPentium G4560</blockquote><br />\n重有粒Celeron D 320<br />\n果時可以谷上3.2, 有D友玩到3.4~6<br />\n<br />\n佢同2500+ 果時係腦場都好受歡迎<br />\nAMD重有粒可以改U<br />\n同埋南北橋散熱 電壓<br />\n其實都幾好玩,以前超頻"},{"pid":"6e7385fabbcf212dceaa3471b1b4786f16fb3578","tid":475814,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T12:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>果時tiny d機又平又多野送</blockquote><br />\n我都係2000年買， 成皮， 但乜柒都包哂<br />\n主機，厚mon(好戇鳩，遲一排就出薄mon),  眼仔， scanner,  printer,  喇叭。<br />\n部野都用到5年</blockquote><br />\n當年送Game RCT1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己第一隻PC game</blockquote><br />\n果時佢同IBM都做緊promotions <br />\n主機加1蚊有 scanner printer mon</blockquote><br />\n咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正條撚, 主機9999 ,全部+1蚊咪成雞野<br />\n果時買電腦真係雞雞聲<br />\n最得意係第一次上網<br />\n56K 撥號連線<br />\n果時internet無而家捉得咁嚴,睇到好多殺人,色情既野"},{"pid":"417eeffb10f073593ca83e1ca01f9b27b81dfd4d","tid":475814,"uid":36325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-22T15:55:18.000Z","msg":"睇黎好多巴打都係2000年果陣開始買電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當初上網仲係56K, 一上網屋企電話就會收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}